Text: RE Lunch on Wednesdaydepo just got canned Ill email again when Im coming down there and hopefully grab lunch Come visit your brother some weekend when Millers band is playing Your children need to see your ancestral roots John Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday September AM To John Scott Subject Re Lunch on Wednesday Yes Let me know where and when John Scott usmanGo To dfreycom cc Subject Lunch on Wednesday PM I have a depo on Weds in the lovely Bayou City Are you available for lunch Ill call Yardbird and Jones John
